("Tofu Stir-Fry", "Indulge in a vibrant and flavorful vegan tofu stir-fry that brings the best of plant-based cuisine to your table. This quick and easy dish features crispy golden tofu, sautéed with a colorful medley of fresh vegetables, such as bell peppers, broccoli, and snap peas, all tossed in a savory soy sauce and ginger-infused marinade. Perfectly seasoned and served over a bed of fluffy rice or quinoa, this wholesome stir-fry is not only packed with protein and nutrition but also bursting with delightful textures and tastes. Enjoy this satisfying meal that’s as delightful to eat as it is to prepare!", "tofu, broccoli, carrot, soy sauce, sesame oil, ginger", 0.50, 3, "Vegan", 20, "https://littlespicejar.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Sesame-Ginger-Tofu-Stir-Fry-1-735x1103.jpeg"),
